http://www.atr.org:80/heritage/p_review/jan96/meese.html 204.71.237.87 19970209180652 text/html 27723
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 18:07:37 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jan-96 22:41:16 GMT
Content-length: 27537
