<P>
<font size="-1">Source: <i> Statistical Abstract of the United States, 1994</i>, Table #938.</font>
<p><hr><p>


<b>7.</b> Number of People in <b>Military Reserves</b><br>
(in thousands, excludes Coast Guard.  At end of fiscal year):
<p><center><table border>
<tr>
<th></th><td>1970</td><td>1980</td><td>1990</td><td>1993</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Reserves</th><td>3,639</td><td>1,349</td><td>1,670</td><td>1,867</td>
</tr></table></center><p>



<font size="-1">Source: <i> Statistical Abstract of the United States, 1994</i>, Table #561.</font>
<p><hr><p>


<b>8.</b> Number of <b>Births and Deaths</b> (in thousands):
<p><center>
<table border>
<tr><th></th><td>1970</td><td>1992</td></tr>
