<TITLE>Town Hall Spotlight: Bosnia - Is It Worth It?</TITLE>

</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">  
<P>

<CENTER><a name="intro"></a> 

<H2>The Bosnia Mission - Is It Worth it?<BR></CENTER></H2>

This week, President Clinton is sending thousands of U.S. Troops to Bosnia to make peace and not everyone agrees on the goals, reasons, or if we should even be in Bosnia.  This week, Town Hall has assembled several pieces of information from around the net and here at Town Hall.  Check back every day for new additions and later in the week, give us your opinion of the Bosnia mission.
<P>


<P>
<P>


<HR>

<P><a name="week"></a>

