http://www.atr.org:80/empower/sp-11175.html 204.71.237.87 19970209183923 text/html 7974
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 18:40:07 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 20:54:54 GMT
