http://www.atr.org:80/pff/people/sfellow.html 204.71.237.87 19970209184051 text/html 10032
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 18:41:35 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:36 GMT
