<p>
<h3>Books and Special Reports</h3><P>


</CENTER>
<HR SIZE = 3 WIDTH = 50%><P>
<P>
From time to time, FRC releases special reports on public policy issues, as well as commemoratives designed to highlight some aspect of our American heritage of family, faith, and freedom.  Citizens interested in a comprehensive blueprint for pro-family public policy, parents interested in educational resources for their children, anyone interested in finding ways to combat a culture hostile to families -- all of these and more are likely to find an FRC booklet that fills the need.
<P>
Please be patient with us as we are trying to get all of our reports 
added to this page.  Check back soon since we will be updating it 
frequently.

<p>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/whois/bauerdoc.html">Gary L. Bauer's Books</A>
