<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/nationalreview/13nov95/al.htm 204.71.237.87 19970209184127 text/html 4941
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 18:42:12 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Dec-95 21:09:49 GMT
