<DOCNO>WT20-B28-135</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA034-000682-B010-219</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/nmp/wr-10-95.html 204.71.237.87 19970209202822 text/html 12890
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 20:29:05 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 16-Nov-95 14:30:31 GMT
