<html>
<head>
<title>Pinkerton to Speak</title>
</head>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/pff/notebook.gif" LINK="#8C1717" VLINK="#545454" ALINK="#FF0000"> <ul><blockquote><a href="/pff"><img src="/pff/pffdoc.gif" align="right" border="0"></a><center>
<h2>James Pinkerton to speak at Brown Bag Luncheon, September 29.</h2>



<h3>The Progress & Freedom Foundation<br>
presents: <br><br></h3>

<h3>James P. Pinkerton</h3>
<h4>to discuss his book,</h4>
<h3><i>What Comes Next:<br>
The End of Big Government-<br>
and the New Paradigm Ahead</i></h3>
on<br>
Friday, September 29, 1995<br><br>
at<br>
12:00 PM<br><br>
for<br>
A Luncheon
hosted by<br>
Joseph E Seagrams & Sons, Inc.<p>

Please join us at the Joseph E. Seagrams & Sons condominium at<br>
